### Changes from 0.8.0 to 1.0.0

#### Features

  - RkObject and object tree ownership
  - RkContinerItem, now continer supports space, RkWidget and RkContainter items
  - Popup widget
  - Hover event
  - RkTransition - linear transition from one value to another, useful for effects
  - RkAction, useful to execute asyncronous actions

#### Improvements

  - RkContianer
  - RkEventQueue
  - RkWidget
  - RkButton
  - events, actions and objects binds

